column5: Here's a couple of fish from a spot about a block from my house.. just pulling off some pics from my cell. Figured I'd share.
Cool. When I saw the Carp I was like..eh...but a Brown...now thats a fish
Good stuff Rich!!  those are some sweet resi browns! bet your happy with the move..
Nothin better than browns in da backyard  Bushart

Very nice Rich. You know, I've been fishing for more than 55 years and I've never caught a brown. Maybe someday, someone will be kind to me and point me in the right direction. They are such a nice looking fish. Thanks for the report.
Beauty BBR! Got ta love a short walk to get fish. Keep up the good work, keep posting and dude, go make yerself a sandwich! Yer fading away! HH
Wow, nice pics man.. can't complain about fishing opporunities that close to home, eh!
Almost a proper carp holding pose, you're getting there ;-)  If someone tells me he catches fish of this quality in his backyard, I would believe he live in paradise.
ditto that haha.  That's a nice brown!
That is one funky lookin' brownie!
